title: 288: Latest draft buzz, Luke Falk & Trent Dilfer interviews
itunes:title: 288: Latest draft buzz, Luke Falk & Trent Dilfer interviews
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks reveal the latest draft buzz and a few deep draft sleepers. DJ also previews his latest Mock Draft (3:06). The guys then talk to Washington State QB prospect Luke Falk (32:38) as well as quarterback guru Trent Dilfer (39:32).
